MARK, YOU GOT TO STOP DRINKING.

35:20.285 --> 35:21.995
LOOK, WE DON'T HAVE MUCH TIME.

35:22.037 --> 35:22.871
THIS IS A GRAND JURY.

35:22.913 --> 35:24.205
I CAN'T GO IN THERE WITH YOU,

35:24.247 --> 35:25.999
BUT I'LL BE OUT HERE

35:24.247 --> 35:25.999
IF YOU NEED TO SPEAK TO ME.

35:26.041 --> 35:29.461
ANSWER THEIR QUESTIONS,

35:26.041 --> 35:29.461
AND YOU'RE HOME FREE.

35:29.502 --> 35:31.129
COME ON.

35:31.170 --> 35:32.255
NOW, GO.

35:32.297 --> 35:34.173
DANNY, I TALKED TO YOU.

35:32.297 --> 35:34.173
I'M --

35:36.802 --> 35:38.553
THE PEOPLE CALL MARK VECTOR

35:36.802 --> 35:38.553
TO THE STAND.

35:38.595 --> 35:41.389
RAISE YOUR RIGHT HAND.

35:41.431 --> 35:43.558
DO YOU SWEAR OR AFFIRM

35:41.431 --> 35:43.558
THAT YOU'LL TELL THE TRUTH,

35:43.600 --> 35:45.435
THE WHOLE TRUTH,

35:43.600 --> 35:45.435
AND NOTHING BUT THE TRUTH?

35:45.477 --> 35:47.395
I DO.

35:47.437 --> 35:48.939
PLEASE BE SEATED.

35:51.817 --> 35:53.944
STATE YOUR NAME AND OCCUPATION.

35:53.986 --> 35:55.236
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

35:55.278 --> 35:57.072
MARK VECTOR,

35:55.278 --> 35:57.072
PRESIDENT AND C.E.O.,

35:57.114 --> 35:59.491
SLAP SHOT INVESTMENTS, LLC.

36:03.996 --> 36:05.163
MR. VECTOR?

36:06.205 --> 36:08.000
MR. VECTOR!

36:08.041 --> 36:10.085
UH, WHAT?

36:10.127 --> 36:12.253
I JUST ASKED YOU

36:10.127 --> 36:12.253
TO TELL THE GRAND JURY

36:12.295 --> 36:14.589
WHAT SLAP SHOT INVESTMENTS IS.

36:14.631 --> 36:16.133
UH...

36:21.262 --> 36:22.305
[ GASPS ]

36:22.347 --> 36:23.556
OH, MY GOSH, YOU'RE MARK VECTOR!

36:23.598 --> 36:25.892
I KNOW A GREAT BAR.

36:23.598 --> 36:25.892
IT'S RIGHT BY MY PLACE.

36:25.934 --> 36:27.727
I SAID, GOOD MORNING.

36:29.187 --> 36:31.230
NO, NO, NO, NO.

36:31.272 --> 36:34.818
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

36:34.860 --> 36:36.862
WAIT A MINUTE, WAIT A MINUTE.

36:38.196 --> 36:39.781
WHAT THE HELL

36:38.196 --> 36:39.781
IS GOING ON HERE, HUH?

36:39.823 --> 36:40.866
MR. VECTOR, SIT DOWN.

36:40.907 --> 36:42.575
NO, NO, NO, COUNSELOR.

36:40.907 --> 36:42.575
THIS IS A SETUP!

36:42.617 --> 36:43.827
THEY -- NO, NO, NO!

36:43.869 --> 36:44.828
TAKE YOUR SEAT,

36:43.869 --> 36:44.828
OR I WILL HAVE YOU REMOVED!

36:44.870 --> 36:46.038
THEY MADE ME THINK

36:44.870 --> 36:46.038
I KILLED HER!

36:46.079 --> 36:47.580
[ SPECTATORS MURMURING ]

36:47.622 --> 36:50.458
AND THIS GUY -- THIS GUY --

36:47.622 --> 36:50.458
HE -- HE'S NOT IN THE FBI!

36:50.500 --> 36:51.793
HE'S HERE TO KILL ME!

36:51.835 --> 36:53.294
WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?!

36:53.336 --> 36:55.463
WHO THE HELL ARE YOU,

36:53.336 --> 36:55.463
YOU SON OF A BITCH?! HUH?!

36:55.505 --> 36:57.549
SO, YOU THINK

36:55.505 --> 36:57.549
I'M SOME KIND OF STUPID GOON

36:57.590 --> 36:58.800
THAT YOU CAN PUSH AROUND?!

36:58.842 --> 36:59.843
HUH?!

36:59.885 --> 37:02.054
WHO DO YOU WORK FOR?!

36:59.885 --> 37:02.054
HUH?! WHO?!

37:02.095 --> 37:03.596
[ GRUNTING ]

37:03.638 --> 37:06.349
Mr. Moreau

37:03.638 --> 37:06.349
would like to speak with you.

37:06.391 --> 37:07.559
YOU SON OF A BITCH!

37:10.645 --> 37:13.106
[ GRUNTING ]

37:13.148 --> 37:15.608
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

37:15.650 --> 37:17.652
-[ TASER CRACKLING ]

37:15.650 --> 37:17.652
-AAH!

37:17.694 --> 37:19.362
[ GRUNTING ]

37:19.404 --> 37:21.573
GET HIM OUT OF HERE.

37:21.614 --> 37:23.533
[ SPECTATORS MURMURING ]

37:23.575 --> 37:26.078
MARK!

37:23.575 --> 37:26.078
WHAT DID YOU DO?!

37:28.287 --> 37:32.209
I THOUGHT YOU DIDN'T LIKE GUNS.

37:32.250 --> 37:33.710
[ AIR SPURTING ]

37:33.752 --> 37:34.794
AIR GUN.

37:34.836 --> 37:36.421
SERIOUSLY?

37:36.462 --> 37:38.381
WHATEVER HAPPENED TO THAT

37:36.462 --> 37:38.381
PRISONER WE WERE TRANSPORTING?

37:38.423 --> 37:39.799
UH, WELL, YOU GUYS SAID

37:39.841 --> 37:41.634
WE COULDN'T JUST TURN HIM IN

37:39.841 --> 37:41.634
TO THE LOCAL COPS, RIGHT,

37:41.676 --> 37:43.469
-'CAUSE HE'D BE A DEAD GUY?

37:41.676 --> 37:43.469
-YEAH.

37:45.055 --> 37:46.056
I DON'T KNOW, SIR,

37:46.098 --> 37:47.390
HE JUST FREAKED OUT

37:46.098 --> 37:47.390
ON THE STAND.

37:47.432 --> 37:49.184
I...

37:49.226 --> 37:50.894
YES, SIR,

37:49.226 --> 37:50.894
I'LL FILE A REPORT RIGHT AWAY.

37:50.936 --> 37:52.812
[ LOUD POUNDING ]

37:57.442 --> 38:00.195
[ MUFFLED SHOUTING ]

38:00.237 --> 38:01.696
"THIS IS A WANTED FUGITIVE.

38:01.738 --> 38:03.656
"PLEASE TAKE HIM

38:01.738 --> 38:03.656
INTO FEDERAL CUSTODY.

38:03.698 --> 38:06.159
"I DON'T WANT YOU

38:03.698 --> 38:06.159
TO GO BACK TO KANSAS.

38:06.201 --> 38:08.494
SINCERELY,

38:06.201 --> 38:08.494
SPECIAL AGENT HAGEN."

38:08.536 --> 38:10.580
[ SIGHS ]

38:10.622 --> 38:11.957
I LOVE THIS JOB.

38:11.998 --> 38:13.833
[ MUFFLED SHOUTING CONTINUES ]

38:15.501 --> 38:18.296
YOU KNOW, I'M REALLY STARTING

38:15.501 --> 38:18.296
TO LIKE TASING PEOPLE.

38:18.337 --> 38:20.048
IS THAT A PROBLEM?

38:20.090 --> 38:22.592
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

38:37.398 --> 38:39.192
MR. FORD.

38:39.234 --> 38:40.777
I'M GLAD YOU MADE IT.

38:40.819 --> 38:41.861
AW, PLEASE.

38:40.819 --> 38:41.861
COME ON.

38:41.903 --> 38:42.946
YOU'RE NOT EVEN TRYING.

38:42.988 --> 38:44.906
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

38:44.948 --> 38:47.492
YOU KNEW VECTOR HAD

38:44.948 --> 38:47.492
MOREAU'S SECRET BANK ACCOUNTS.

38:47.533 --> 38:49.119
YOU KNEW THEY WERE ENCRYPTED.

38:49.161 --> 38:50.829
YOU EVEN KNEW THAT THE KEY WAS

38:50.870 --> 38:52.705
SOMEWHERE HERE

38:50.870 --> 38:52.705
IN VECTOR'S OFFICE.

38:52.747 --> 38:55.167
BUT A BUNCH OF DIRTY COPS WERE

38:52.747 --> 38:55.167
CAMPED OUT, WAITING TO KILL HIM,

38:55.208 --> 38:57.418
SO YOU CAME UP WITH A PLAN --

38:57.460 --> 38:59.921
HAVE US GET THE CODES

38:57.460 --> 38:59.921
FROM VECTOR

38:59.963 --> 39:01.756
AND THEN SEND THE COPS

38:59.963 --> 39:01.756
TO KILL US ALL.

39:01.798 --> 39:05.135
WELL, TO BE FAIR,

39:01.798 --> 39:05.135
I DIDN'T COUNT ON THE SNIPER.

39:05.177 --> 39:07.720
HE WAS AN OUTSIDE CONTRACTOR.

39:07.762 --> 39:10.682
IT'S A SHAME YOU DIDN'T GET

39:07.762 --> 39:10.682
HIS ACCOUNT NUMBERS.

39:10.723 --> 39:12.517
OH, BUT I DID.

39:12.558 --> 39:14.519
YEAH.

39:12.558 --> 39:14.519
THEY'RE RIGHT BEHIND YOU.

39:18.940 --> 39:22.902
YOU SEE, VECTOR...

39:18.940 --> 39:22.902
HAS A PROBLEM.

39:22.944 --> 39:25.822
WHEN HE GETS ANGRY, HE SEES RED.

39:25.864 --> 39:27.657
AND THAT TURNED OUT TO BE

39:25.864 --> 39:27.657
THE KEY TO THE CODE.

39:27.699 --> 39:29.659
NOW, WHEN PHOTOGRAPHS

39:27.699 --> 39:29.659
ARE DIGITIZED TO A COMPUTER,

39:29.701 --> 39:31.911
EVERY SHADE OF COLOR

39:29.701 --> 39:31.911
IS ASSIGNED A NUMBER.

39:31.953 --> 39:34.580
IF YOU TAKE TWO

39:31.953 --> 39:34.580
OTHERWISE IDENTICAL PHOTOS,

39:34.622 --> 39:36.749
WITH TWO DIFFERENT

39:34.622 --> 39:36.749
COLOR SCHEMES,

39:36.791 --> 39:38.877
COMPUTE THE DIFFERENCE...

39:38.918 --> 39:40.295
YOU GOT A CODE.

39:40.337 --> 39:41.462
EXCUSE ME.

39:41.504 --> 39:42.463
[ SNIFFLES ]

39:42.505 --> 39:44.132
-OH.

39:42.505 --> 39:44.132
-OH, LOOK AT THAT.

39:44.174 --> 39:45.842
YOU LOOK LIKE

39:44.174 --> 39:45.842
BARNEY THE DINOSAUR.

39:45.884 --> 39:47.886
YEAH, UH,

39:45.884 --> 39:47.886
THE COLOR'S A LITTLE BIT OFF.

39:49.512 --> 39:52.598
GUYS, I SEE HIS PHONE.

39:52.640 --> 39:54.392
[ MACHINE-GUN FIRE ]

39:58.521 --> 39:59.981
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

40:00.023 --> 40:01.440
AND THERE IT IS.

40:01.482 --> 40:03.609
[ BEEPING ]

40:08.573 --> 40:11.201
AND NOW THEY'RE MINE.

40:13.119 --> 40:14.579
I'M GONNA MAKE ONE WITHDRAWAL

40:14.620 --> 40:18.083
TO GET A HOCKEY FAN

40:14.620 --> 40:18.083
HIS LIFE SAVINGS BACK...

40:18.124 --> 40:20.168
AND THEN I AM GONNA USE

40:18.124 --> 40:20.168
THESE ACCOUNTS

40:20.210 --> 40:22.254
TO TAKE DOWN DAMIEN MOREAU...

40:22.295 --> 40:25.298
ON MY TERMS...WITHOUT YOU.

40:25.340 --> 40:27.384
OUR DEAL IS OVER.

40:27.425 --> 40:30.636
AND YOU COME AFTER MY TEAM,

40:27.425 --> 40:30.636
I WILL COME AFTER YOU.

40:30.678 --> 40:34.307
AND I ASSURE YOU,

40:34.349 --> 40:37.102
I AM MORE THAN THE MAN

40:34.349 --> 40:37.102
YOU THOUGHT I WAS.

40:44.901 --> 40:46.819
[ CELLPHONE DIALING ]

40:46.861 --> 40:48.196
IT WORKED.

40:48.238 --> 40:50.907
HE'S GOING AFTER MOREAU

40:48.238 --> 40:50.907
WITHOUT US.

40:50.949 --> 40:53.159
OUR HANDS ARE CLEAN.

40:56.704 --> 40:58.790
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

41:03.795 --> 41:05.130
[ DOOR OPENS ]

41:08.883 --> 41:09.884
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

41:09.926 --> 41:12.304
MAKE IT TWO.

41:12.345 --> 41:13.888
[ SIGHS ]

41:13.930 --> 41:15.932
THAT ISN'T TO TOAST

41:13.930 --> 41:15.932
OUR VICTORY, IS IT?

41:15.974 --> 41:18.851
MAKING ANOTHER ENEMY IS

41:15.974 --> 41:18.851
HARDLY SOMETHING TO CELEBRATE.

41:18.893 --> 41:20.561
OH, MOREAU TRIED TO KILL US.

41:20.603 --> 41:23.356
NO, HE TRIED TO KILL VECTOR,

41:20.603 --> 41:23.356
AND WE GOT IN THE WAY.

41:23.398 --> 41:25.775
IF ANYONE DESERVES OUR WRATH,

41:23.398 --> 41:25.775
IT'S THE ITALIAN.

41:25.817 --> 41:27.319
NO, THIS IS MUCH BIGGER

41:25.817 --> 41:27.319
THAN THE ITALIAN.

41:30.655 --> 41:33.408
NATE, LET'S GET

41:30.655 --> 41:33.408
ONE THING STRAIGHT.

41:33.450 --> 41:35.534
AS OF THIS MOMENT,

41:33.450 --> 41:35.534
WE GO AFTER MOREAU,

41:35.576 --> 41:37.370
IT'S A CHOICE, NOT A NECESSITY.

41:37.412 --> 41:38.621
YOU'RE RIGHT.

41:38.663 --> 41:40.915
BUT WE'VE NEVER BEEN

41:38.663 --> 41:40.915
IN THIS SITUATION BEFORE.

41:40.957 --> 41:43.501
I MEAN, WE HAVE A CHANCE

41:40.957 --> 41:43.501
TO TAKE OUT DAMIEN MOREAU

41:43.542 --> 41:45.211
BEFORE HE CAUSES MORE DAMAGE.

41:45.253 --> 41:47.005
WE DIDN'T CHOOSE THIS FIGHT,

41:47.046 --> 41:49.674
BUT WE'RE IN IT

41:47.046 --> 41:49.674
AND WE SHOULD SEE IT THROUGH.

41:52.802 --> 41:55.472
TO VICTORY, THEN.

41:59.142 --> 42:00.685
[ GLASSES CLINK ]

42:05.190 --> 42:07.066
[ SIGHS ]
